headline: MetLife (MET) Valuation Review as New Petstablished Partnership Expands Its Pet Insurance Reach
summary: MetLife (MET) just quietly expanded its footprint in the fast growing pet insurance space by partnering with Petstablished so adopters can bolt coverage onto adoption fees right at the shelter checkout. See our latest analysis for MetLife. That push into pet insurance comes as MetLife’s 1 month share price return of 9.5 percent has outpaced its modest year to date gain, while its 5 year total shareholder return of 107.89 percent signals steady, long term wealth creation and building...

headline: MetLife Expands Pet Insurance Reach Through Petstablished Partnership
summary: MET is embedding pet insurance into shelter adoptions via Petstablished, letting adopters bundle coverage into fees and protect pets from day one.

headline: Carla Harris on the Board's Most Crucial Task: CEO Succession
summary: Inside the Boardroom: Carla Harris, a board member at Walmart, Cummins, and MetLife and Senior Client Advisor at Morgan Stanley, joins WSJ's Emily Glazer to analyze the critical role of CEO succession planning in the modern boardroom. Recorded on Nov. 10, 2025.
